### Step 2

Message is sent to Kafka Broker

```text id="nq8wxy"
localhost:9092
```

---

### Step 3

Kafka writes it to one of the partitions

Example:

```text id="ux7ohw"
orders

Partition 0
Offset 0

Partition 1
Offset 0

Partition 2
Offset 0
```

---

### Step 4

Kafka acknowledges receipt

Producer continues.

